  {
    question: 'What makes an effective independent non-executive director?',
    answer: 'Effective non-executive directors combine independence with industry insight. My approach to non-executive director roles emphasises constructive challenge, strategic contribution, and rigorous oversight. The IoD Ambassador status and dual Fellowship credentials (FCMI + FRSPH) demonstrate commitment to board effectiveness and governance excellence that modern boards require.'
